  01 Nov 2006; Federico Fissore <federico@fsfe.org> ChangeLog:
  Because of the new icu4j 3.{4.6} ebuilds, xom now depends on ~icu4j-3.0
  instead of a generic icu4j

  05 Oct 2006; Gustavo Zacarias <gustavoz@gentoo.org> xom-1.0-r1.ebuild,
  xom-1.0-r2.ebuild:
  Dropping sparc keywords, see #96229

*xom-1.0-r2 (15 Aug 2006)

  15 Aug 2006; Krzysiek Pawlik <nelchael@gentoo.org> +xom-1.0-r2.ebuild:
  Migrated to new Java build system.

  09 Dec 2005; Joshua Nichols <nichoj@gentoo.org> xom-1.0-r1.ebuild:
  Fixed invalid atom.

  09 Dec 2005; Joshua Nichols <nichoj@gentoo.org> xom-1.0-r1.ebuild:
  Loosened xerces dependency, in preparation for a new xerces release.

  09 Jul 2005; Thomas Matthijs <axxo@gentoo.org> xom-1.0-r1.ebuild:
  fix deps, some cleanup

  12 Jun 2005; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org> xom-1.0-r1.ebuild:
  Added ~sparc keyword wrt bug #95859.

*xom-1.0-r1 (04 Jun 2005)

  04 Jun 2005; Jan Brinkmann <luckyduck@gentoo.org> -xom-1.0.ebuild,
  +xom-1.0-r1.ebuild:
  Updated reference to servletapi-2.3, we dont install a versioned servletapi
  jar any longer.

  28 Apr 2005; Jan Brinkmann <luckyduck@gentoo.org> xom-1.0.ebuild,
  -xom-1.0_beta5.ebuild, -xom-1.0_beta6.ebuild:
  1.0 stable on amd64, ppc and x86. did some cleanup and introduced support for
  the source useflag

*xom-1.0 (21 Jan 2005)

  21 Jan 2005; Jan Brinkmann <luckyduck@gentoo.org> +xom-1.0.ebuild:
  new version. fixes bug #78860

  03 Nov 2004; Thomas Matthijs <axxo@gentoo.org> xom-1.0_beta5.ebuild,
  xom-1.0_beta6.ebuild:
  depend on app-arch/unzip

  22 Oct 2004; Dylan Carlson <absinthe@gentoo.org> xom-1.0_beta5.ebuild,
  xom-1.0_beta6.ebuild:
  Keywords ~amd64.

  18 Oct 2004; David Holm <dholm@gentoo.org> xom-1.0_beta6.ebuild:
  Added to ~ppc.

  16 Oct 2004; Thomas Matthijs <axxo@gentoo.org> xom-1.0_beta5.ebuild,
  xom-1.0_beta6.ebuild:
  use java-pkg_dohtml instead of dohtml to also install the package-list in
  case of api docs: #50740

*xom-1.0_beta6 (07 Oct 2004)

  07 Oct 2004; Thomas Matthijs <axxo@gentoo.org> +xom-1.0_beta6.ebuild:
  Version bump, Thanks too Carsten Frewert <gentoo@frewert.de> for the patch,
  #66610

*xom-1.0_beta5 (19 Sep 2004)

  19 Sep 2004; Thomas Matthijs <axxo@gentoo.org> -xom-1.0.14.ebuild,
  +xom-1.0_beta5.ebuild:
  version bump, and doesn't use packed jars anymore

  02 Jun 2004; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> xom-1.0.14.ebuild:
  Fix use invocation

  10 Feb 2004; Adrian Almenar <strider@gentoo.org> xom-1.0.14.ebuild:
  Removed alpha keyword.

*xom-1.0.14 (19 May 2003)

  19 May 2003; Dylan Carlson <absinthe@gentoo.org> xom-1.0.14.ebuild:
  Initial import.  Thanks to Ian Phillips <ianp@ianp.org> in bug # 21242
  for the submission.
